{"tid":1199594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣女子落街買KFC外賣 遭紅van撞斃","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T17:30:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8a28ff9acdca0ab6385080e7b6aa8aef22e120b8","tid":1199594,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190610/large/1560174161_5389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190610%2Flarge%2F1560174161_5389.jpg&h=3a92972c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190610/large/1560174161_5e17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190610%2Flarge%2F1560174161_5e17.jpg&h=37b1c54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣發生奪命交通意外！晚上7時許，一名50多歲女子外出買KFC外賣，其間沿馬坑涌道返家時，遭一輛由九龍城道左轉入的紅色小巴撞倒。<br />\n<br />\n女子被撞飛數米倒卧地上，躺在血泊中，昏迷不醒，外賣亦散落一地，門牙飛脫，救護員到場將女子送往醫院搶救，可惜最終不治，警方正調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"09986e8ab44497b94707deb08a66e604579820bc","tid":1199594,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190610/59700175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59700175&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=795457f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59700175&h=1034abef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190610/59700175</a>"},{"pid":"399d4852338b6049b9e430a05e7afa79993ccfb1","tid":1199594,"uid":26106,"like":426,"dislike":7,"score":419,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"我願意用10隻香港警犬條命換返呢個女人條命<img src=\"/assets/face